{
  "video_id": "CijsvAGU6-c",
  "title": "Carlo Ratti: Architecture that senses and responds",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "Good afternoon, everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got something to show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "Think about this as a pixel, a flying pixel."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "This is what we call, in our lab, sensible design."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you a bit about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "Now if you take this picture -- I&#39;m Italian originally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "and every boy in Italy grows up"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "with this picture on the wall of his bedroom --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "but the reason I&#39;m showing you this"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "is that something very interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "happened in Formula 1 racing"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "over the past couple of decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "Now some time ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "if you wanted to win a Formula 1 race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "you take a budget, and you bet your budget"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "on a good driver and a good car."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "And if the car and the driver were good enough, then you&#39;d win the race."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Now today, if you want to win the race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "actually you need also something like this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "something that monitors the car in real time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "has a few thousand sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "collecting information from the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "transmitting this information into the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "and then processing it"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "and using it in order to go back to the car with decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "and changing things in real time"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "as information is collected."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "This is what, in engineering terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "you would call a real time control system."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "And basically, it&#39;s a system made of two components --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "a sensing and an actuating component."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "What is interesting today"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "is that real time control systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "are starting to enter into our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "Our cities, over the past few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "just have been blanketed"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "with networks, electronics."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re becoming like computers in open air."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "And, as computers in open air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re starting to respond in a different way"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "to be able to be sensed and to be actuated."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "If we fix cities, actually it&#39;s a big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "Just as an aside, I wanted to mention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "cities are only two percent of the Earth&#39;s crust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "but they are 50 percent of the world&#39;s population."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "They are 75 percent of the energy consumption --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "up to 80 percent of CO2 emissions."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "So if we&#39;re able to do something with cities, that&#39;s a big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "Beyond cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "all of this sensing and actuating"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "is entering our everyday objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s from an exhibition that"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "Paola Antonelli is organizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "at MoMA later this year, during the summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Talk to Me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "Well our objects, our environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "is starting to talk back to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "In a certain sense, it&#39;s almost as if every atom out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "were becoming both a sensor and an actuator."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "And that is radically changing the interaction we have as humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "with the environment out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "In a certain sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s almost as if the old dream of Michelangelo ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "you know, when Michelangelo sculpted the Moses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "at the end it said that he took the hammer, threw it at the Moses --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "actually you can still see a small chip underneath --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "and said, shouted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "\"Perché non parli? Why don&#39;t you talk?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "Well today, for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "our environment is starting to talk back to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll show just a few examples --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "again, with this idea of sensing our environment and actuating it."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s starting with sensing."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "Well, the first project I wanted to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "is actually one of the first projects by our lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "It was four and a half years ago in Italy."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "And what we did there"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "was actually use a new type of network at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "that had been deployed all across the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a cellphone network --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "and use anonymous and aggregated information from that network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s collected anyway by the operator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "in order to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "how the city works."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "The summer was a lucky summer -- 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s when Italy won the soccer World Cup."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "Some of you might remember, it was Italy and France playing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "and then Zidane at the end, the headbutt."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "And anyway, Italy won at the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "Now look at what happened that day"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "just by monitoring activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "happening on the network."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "Here you see the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "You see the Colosseum in the middle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "the river Tiber."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s morning, before the match."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "You see the timeline on the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "Early afternoon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "people here and there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "making calls and moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "The match begins -- silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "France scores. Italy scores."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "Halftime, people make a quick call and go to the bathroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "Second half. End of normal time."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "First overtime, second."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "Zidane, the headbutt in a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "Italy wins. Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "Well, that night, everybody went to celebrate in the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "You saw the big peak."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "The following day, again everybody went to the center"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "to meet the winning team"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "and the prime minister at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "And then everybody moved down."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "You see the image of the place called Circo Massimo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "where, since Roman times, people go to celebrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "to have a big party, and you see the peak at the end of the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s just one example of how we can sense the city today"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "in a way that we couldn&#39;t have done"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "just a few years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "Another quick example about sensing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not about people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "but about things we use and consume."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "Well today, we know everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "about where our objects come from."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "This is a map that shows you"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "all the chips that form a Mac computer, how they came together."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "But we know very little about where things go."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "So in this project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "we actually developed some small tags"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "to track trash as it moves through the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "So we actually started with a number of volunteers"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "who helped us in Seattle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "just over a year ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "to tag what they were throwing away --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "different types of things, as you can see here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "things they would throw away anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "Then we put a little chip, little tag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "onto the trash"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "and then started following it."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "Here are the results we just obtained."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "From Seattle ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "after one week."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "With this information we realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a lot of inefficiencies in the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "We can actually do the same thing with much less energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "This data was not available before."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a lot of wasted transportation and convoluted things happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "But the other thing is that we believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "that if we see every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "that the cup we&#39;re throwing away, it doesn&#39;t disappear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s still somewhere on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "And the plastic bottle we&#39;re throwing away every day still stays there."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "And if we show that to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "then we can also promote some behavioral change."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "So that was the reason for the project."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "My colleague at MIT, Assaf Biderman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "he could tell you much more about sensing"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "and many other wonderful things we can do with sensing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "but I wanted to go to the second part we discussed at the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 453260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s actuating our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 453260.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "And the first project"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "is something we did a couple of years ago in Zaragoza, Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "It started with a question by the mayor of the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "who came to us saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "that Spain and Southern Europe have a beautiful tradition"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "of using water in public space, in architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "And the question was: How could technology, new technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "be added to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "And one of the ideas that was developed at MIT in a workshop"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "was, imagine this pipe, and you&#39;ve got valves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "solenoid valves, taps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "opening and closing."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "You create like a water curtain with pixels made of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 488260.0,
      "text": "If those pixels fall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 488260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "you can write on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "you can show patterns, images, text."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "And even you can approach it, and it will open up"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 494260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "to let you jump through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "as you see in this image."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "Well, we presented this to Mayor Belloch."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 500260.0,
      "end_time": 502260.0,
      "text": "He liked it very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 504260.0,
      "text": "And we got a commission to design a building"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 504260.0,
      "end_time": 506260.0,
      "text": "at the entrance of the expo."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "We called it Digital Water Pavilion."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "The whole building is made of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no doors or windows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "but when you approach it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "it will open up to let you in."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "The roof also is covered with water."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 537260.0,
      "end_time": 539260.0,
      "text": "And if there&#39;s a bit of wind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 539260.0,
      "end_time": 542260.0,
      "text": "if you want to minimize splashing, you can actually lower the roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 544260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "Or you could close the building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "and the whole architecture will disappear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "like in this case."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 552260.0,
      "text": "You know, these days, you always get images during the winter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 554260.0,
      "text": "when they take the roof down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 554260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "of people who have been there and said, \"They demolished the building.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "No, they didn&#39;t demolish it, just when it goes down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "the architecture almost disappears."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 564260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the building working."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 564260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "You see the person puzzled about what was going on inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 569260.0,
      "text": "And here was myself trying not to get wet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 569260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "testing the sensors that open the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "Well, I should tell you now what happened one night"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "when all of the sensors stopped working."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 580260.0,
      "text": "But actually that night, it was even more fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 580260.0,
      "end_time": 582260.0,
      "text": "All the kids from Zaragoza came to the building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 582260.0,
      "end_time": 585260.0,
      "text": "because the way of engaging with the building became something different."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 585260.0,
      "end_time": 588260.0,
      "text": "Not anymore a building that would open up to let you in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 588260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "but a building that would still make cuts and holes through the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "and you had to jump without getting wet."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "(Video) (Crowd Noise)"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "And that was, for us, was very interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 611260.0,
      "text": "because, as architects, as engineers, as designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 611260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "we always think about how people will use the things we design."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "But then reality&#39;s always unpredictable."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 619260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the beauty of doing things"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "that are used and interact with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 623260.0,
      "text": "Here is an image then of the building"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "with the physical pixels, the pixels made of water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "and then projections on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 630260.0,
      "text": "And this is what led us to think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 630260.0,
      "end_time": 632260.0,
      "text": "the following project I&#39;ll show you now."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 632260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s, imagine those pixels could actually start flying."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 637260.0,
      "text": "Imagine you could have small helicopters"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 637260.0,
      "end_time": 639260.0,
      "text": "that move in the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 639260.0,
      "end_time": 642260.0,
      "text": "and then each of them with a small pixel in changing lights --"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 642260.0,
      "end_time": 645260.0,
      "text": "almost as a cloud that can move in space."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 645260.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "Here is the video."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 653260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 653260.0,
      "end_time": 656260.0,
      "text": "So imagine one helicopter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 656260.0,
      "end_time": 659260.0,
      "text": "like the one we saw before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 661260.0,
      "end_time": 664260.0,
      "text": "moving with others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 664260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "in synchrony."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 669260.0,
      "text": "So you can have this cloud."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 675260.0,
      "end_time": 679260.0,
      "text": "You can have a kind of flexible screen or display, like this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 679260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "a regular configuration in two dimensions."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 689260.0,
      "end_time": 692260.0,
      "text": "Or in regular, but in three dimensions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 694260.0,
      "text": "where the thing that changes is the light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 694260.0,
      "end_time": 696260.0,
      "text": "not the pixels&#39; position."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 706260.0,
      "end_time": 708260.0,
      "text": "You can play with a different type."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "Imagine your screen could just appear"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "in different scales or sizes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "different types of resolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 725260.0,
      "end_time": 727260.0,
      "text": "But then the whole thing can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 727260.0,
      "end_time": 729260.0,
      "text": "just a 3D cloud of pixels"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 729260.0,
      "end_time": 732260.0,
      "text": "that you can approach and move through it"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 732260.0,
      "end_time": 735260.0,
      "text": "and see from many, many directions."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 735260.0,
      "end_time": 737260.0,
      "text": "Here is the real Flyfire"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 737260.0,
      "end_time": 741260.0,
      "text": "control and going down to form the regular grid as before."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 741260.0,
      "end_time": 744260.0,
      "text": "When you turn on the light, actually you see this. So the same as we saw before."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 744260.0,
      "end_time": 746260.0,
      "text": "And imagine each of them then controlled by people."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 746260.0,
      "end_time": 748260.0,
      "text": "You can have each pixel"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 748260.0,
      "end_time": 750260.0,
      "text": "having an input that comes from people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 750260.0,
      "end_time": 752260.0,
      "text": "from people&#39;s movement, or so and so."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 752260.0,
      "end_time": 755260.0,
      "text": "I want to show you something here for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 755260.0,
      "end_time": 757260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been working with Roberto Bolle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 757260.0,
      "end_time": 759260.0,
      "text": "one of today&#39;s top ballet dancers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 759260.0,
      "end_time": 761260.0,
      "text": "the étoile at Metropolitan in New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 761260.0,
      "end_time": 763260.0,
      "text": "and La Scala in Milan --"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 763260.0,
      "end_time": 765260.0,
      "text": "and actually captured his movement in 3D"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 765260.0,
      "end_time": 768260.0,
      "text": "in order to use it as an input for Flyfire."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 768260.0,
      "end_time": 771260.0,
      "text": "And here you can see Roberto dancing."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 773260.0,
      "end_time": 775260.0,
      "text": "You see on the left the pixels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 775260.0,
      "end_time": 777260.0,
      "text": "the different resolutions being captured."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 777260.0,
      "end_time": 779260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s both 3D scanning in real time"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 779260.0,
      "end_time": 782260.0,
      "text": "and motion capture."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 783260.0,
      "end_time": 786260.0,
      "text": "So you can reconstruct a whole movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 790260.0,
      "end_time": 793260.0,
      "text": "You can go all the way through."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 796260.0,
      "end_time": 798260.0,
      "text": "But then, once we have the pixels, then you can play with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 798260.0,
      "end_time": 801260.0,
      "text": "and play with color and movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 801260.0,
      "end_time": 804260.0,
      "text": "and gravity and rotation."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 804260.0,
      "end_time": 806260.0,
      "text": "So we want to use this as one of the possible inputs"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 806260.0,
      "end_time": 808260.0,
      "text": "for Flyfire."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 827260.0,
      "end_time": 829260.0,
      "text": "I wanted to show you the last project we are working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 829260.0,
      "end_time": 831260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something we&#39;re working on for the London Olympics."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 831260.0,
      "end_time": 833260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called The Cloud."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 833260.0,
      "end_time": 835260.0,
      "text": "And the idea here is, imagine, again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 835260.0,
      "end_time": 837260.0,
      "text": "we can involve people"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 837260.0,
      "end_time": 840260.0,
      "text": "in doing something and changing our environment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 840260.0,
      "end_time": 842260.0,
      "text": "almost to impart what we call cloud raising --"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 842260.0,
      "end_time": 844260.0,
      "text": "like barn raising, but with a cloud."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 844260.0,
      "end_time": 848260.0,
      "text": "Imagine you can have everybody make a small donation for one pixel."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 848260.0,
      "end_time": 850260.0,
      "text": "And I think what is remarkable"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 850260.0,
      "end_time": 852260.0,
      "text": "that has happened over the past couple of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 852260.0,
      "end_time": 854260.0,
      "text": "is that, over the past couple of decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 854260.0,
      "end_time": 857260.0,
      "text": "we went from the physical world to the digital one."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 857260.0,
      "end_time": 859260.0,
      "text": "This has been digitizing everything, knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 859260.0,
      "end_time": 861260.0,
      "text": "and making that accessible through the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 861260.0,
      "end_time": 863260.0,
      "text": "Now today, for the first time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 863260.0,
      "end_time": 865260.0,
      "text": "and the Obama campaign showed us this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 865260.0,
      "end_time": 867260.0,
      "text": "we can go from the digital world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 867260.0,
      "end_time": 869260.0,
      "text": "from the self-organizing power of networks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 869260.0,
      "end_time": 871260.0,
      "text": "to the physical one."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 871260.0,
      "end_time": 873260.0,
      "text": "This can be, in our case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 873260.0,
      "end_time": 875260.0,
      "text": "we want to use it for designing and doing a symbol."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 875260.0,
      "end_time": 877260.0,
      "text": "That means something built in a city."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 877260.0,
      "end_time": 879260.0,
      "text": "But tomorrow it can be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 879260.0,
      "end_time": 882260.0,
      "text": "in order to tackle today&#39;s pressing challenges --"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 882260.0,
      "end_time": 884260.0,
      "text": "think about climate change or CO2 emissions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 884260.0,
      "end_time": 887260.0,
      "text": "how we can go from the digital world to the physical one."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 887260.0,
      "end_time": 889260.0,
      "text": "So the idea that we can actually involve people"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 889260.0,
      "end_time": 891260.0,
      "text": "in doing this thing together, collectively."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 891260.0,
      "end_time": 894260.0,
      "text": "The cloud is a cloud, again, made of pixels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 894260.0,
      "end_time": 896260.0,
      "text": "in the same way as the real cloud"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 896260.0,
      "end_time": 898260.0,
      "text": "is a cloud made of particles."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 898260.0,
      "end_time": 900260.0,
      "text": "And those particles are water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 900260.0,
      "end_time": 902260.0,
      "text": "where our cloud is a cloud of pixels."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 902260.0,
      "end_time": 905260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a physical structure in London, but covered with pixels."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 905260.0,
      "end_time": 907260.0,
      "text": "You can move inside, have different types of experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 907260.0,
      "end_time": 909260.0,
      "text": "You can actually see from underneath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 909260.0,
      "end_time": 911260.0,
      "text": "sharing the main moments"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 911260.0,
      "end_time": 914260.0,
      "text": "for the Olympics in 2012 and beyond,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 914260.0,
      "end_time": 918260.0,
      "text": "and really using it as a way to connect with the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 918260.0,
      "end_time": 922260.0,
      "text": "So both the physical cloud in the sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 922260.0,
      "end_time": 925260.0,
      "text": "and something you can go to the top [of],"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 925260.0,
      "end_time": 927260.0,
      "text": "like London&#39;s new mountaintop."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 927260.0,
      "end_time": 929260.0,
      "text": "You can enter inside it."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 929260.0,
      "end_time": 932260.0,
      "text": "And a kind of new digital beacon for the night --"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 932260.0,
      "end_time": 934260.0,
      "text": "but most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 934260.0,
      "end_time": 937260.0,
      "text": "a new type of experience for anybody who will go to the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 937260.0,
      "end_time": 939260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 939260.0,
      "end_time": 941260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}